style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>You can customize game behavior by setting optio=
ns in
the Game Options screen (O key). This includes display and audio settings, =
as
well as game automation and message display settings.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Display Settings<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Here you can control =
the
scroll speed in the main view. Move the slider to the left to make scrolling
slower, move it to the right to speed up scrolling.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>You can also control =
the
zooming speed in the main view. Move the slider to the left to make zooming
slower, move it to the right to speed up zooming.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Star Density controls=
 how
many stars appear in the background star field of the main view. Move the
slider to the left for less stars, move to the right for more stars. Note t=
hat
the background star field is purely for appearance &#8211; it has no functi=
on
in the game.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Sound Volume<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>The music and sound e=
ffect
volumes can be increased by moving the appropriate slider to the right. To =
make
sounds quieter, move the slider to the left.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'tab-stops:78.45pt'><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-=
weight:
normal'><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-no-pr=
oof:
yes'>Auto Save</span><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'><span style=3D'mso-ta=
b-count:
1'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Here you can choose t=
o have
the game automatically save at specified intervals.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-no-proof:yes'>Loaded
Games Are Paused<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Enable this if you wa=
nt
loaded games to start off paused. This can be useful if you have very large
games that take a while to load.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Mouse scroll-wheel behavior<o:p></o:p>=
</span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Choose how the mouse
scroll-wheel functions by selecting from this list.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l=
