an
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>No movement</span></b><span style=3D'mso-no-proo=
f:yes'>:
scrolling the mouse wheel does not move the main view<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
